  "detailed_description": "<strong>「Bargaining」as the core, with the cyberpunk style of art performance, 《lower? higher!》 wants to provide you with a different experience of pawnshop operation.<br>You will trade with customers with different needs, and in the process, you can speculate on the psychology of the customer, change the properties of the product, or directly pray to the dice god -- these various business methods can help you achieve the maximum profit of the pawnshop.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913660/extras/f597c1d4fd3683b90c774a8865efe2c6.webp?t=1745035963\" width=630 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913660/extras/576412c07abffb8a9da3e391e3b7d3da.poster.avif?t=1745035963\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913660/extras/576412c07abffb8a9da3e391e3b7d3da.webm?t=1745035963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913660/extras/576412c07abffb8a9da3e391e3b7d3da.mp4?t=1745035963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913660/extras/662d3947e651feb625b34bd2626fb6ed.avif?t=1745035963\" width=614 height=132 /></span><br><strong>All kinds of guests have different personalities and preferences, and it is not easy to entertain them. It is possible to achieve the purpose of trade by mobilizing different bargaining strategies.<br>The same product in different customers also have different valuation, as soon as possible to sell or wait for a predestined person? It's up to you.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"h